transcript:

Executive: Hello
Customer: Haan?
Executive: Sir, mai Govind bol raha hu, Govind Kushwaha.
Customer: Haan ji, bataiye.
Customer: Aapke bhi alag phone jaati hai kya? Haan?
Executive: Complaint wale to alag hote hain.
Customer: Mere paas hi call aayega aapka, tabhi to maine detail li hai na aap se complaint open karne ke liye.
Executive: Aur kuch hai detail mein, kya chahiye aapko?
Executive: Nahi, aur kuch nahi hai. Hum hi complaint open karenge aapki.
Customer: Theek hai, theek hai.
